1 - As a teacher I need to provide bio info about myself
2 - As a teacher I need to provide contact info about myself
3 - As a teacher I need to be able to publish a schedule
4 - As a potential student I need to be able to register as a student
5 - As a student I need to be able to select an available lesson time
6 - As a student I need to be able to securely logon
7 - As a teacher I need to be able to securely logon
8 - As an admin I need to be able to manage multiple clients (tenants)